, adult male, collected in 1862 by James McLeannan, presumably near the 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:430787C0A805FFDAFC87FEFCFB030DDA:CE71600DA805FFDAFC23FD96FBC70B43" box="[950,1146,579,601]" country="Panama" name="Lion Hill station" pageId="29" pageNumber="29">Lion Hill station</location>
